Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:22.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}你已再也不會回到我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:28.20,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}留下的傷痕  讓我近乎崩壞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.26,0:21:33.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}相連的溫暖  令我不願回想
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.34,0:21:39.85,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}被塗滿的畫布  消散的香水味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.93,0:21:45.82,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}即使走向毀滅是無可避免的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.94,0:21:50.64,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}我也願意相信  這份愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.55,0:21:57.32,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}在痛苦中尋求羈絆  與世界纏繞交織
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.40,0:22:02.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}隱藏起指間的顫抖  朝著明天的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:08.83,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}如果這是你的願望  我願將性命相交
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:11.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}當扣下污濁的扳機之時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:17.25,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}你與我同在  我將改變你的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:21.22,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,500)\blur4}向著這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,TXT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:06.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:09.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和那時比起來好走多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.25,0:00:17.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該就是那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.69,0:00:39.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,致我的摯友  周防天音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在讀這封信就說明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.99,0:00:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事故已經過去了數年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.97,0:00:47.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而你也已經冷靜下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.23,0:00:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定很想知道這裡究竟發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才打開了這個箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先把結果先簡單地告知於你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.15,0:00:58.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全部人都病死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原因是廣岡同學所患有的皮膚疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.91,0:01:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家服用了含有毒素的湯之後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.80,0:01:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都患上了急性內臟疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後全都病死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然  沒有吃那些肉的你得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就結果而言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也許真正救你的人是廣岡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  就我對你的了解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.14,0:01:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定認為自己獲救是多虧了挺身而出的好友風見一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,並且一邊流著淚一邊滿懷感激吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼作為你救命恩人的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:44.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我的弟弟身陷痛苦之中的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.01,0:01:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能幫助他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:53.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的弟弟雄二既膽小又愛哭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:56.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要說優點的話  就只有為人比較溫柔這點了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:02:00.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過對我而言  卻是我無可替代的可愛弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我僅有的牽掛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你能守護我的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.40,0:02:15.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  要是還活著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,期盼我們的再次重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:25.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你人生最好的摯友  風見一姬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.15,0:02:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一姬到底怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,活著嗎  還是死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.44,0:02:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  這封信的確很有一姬的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:45.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是敵不過一姬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.50,0:02:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡和當初一樣  幾乎沒有改變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沿著那個方向走三個小時就可以抵達公路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那也得當時有那條路才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話我還是很害怕你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只是一味地逃避並不能解決問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:25.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我放棄逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「只有我活了下來  原諒我」這種話我不會說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道想要獲得原諒這個想法就是很厚顏無恥的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不會道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為交換  之後我會一直感謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家  謝謝你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.86,0:03:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坂下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,蒔菜打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.21,0:04:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼呢  周防天音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.98,0:04:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在等著你回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有在聽嗎  天音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我呢  是坂下千秋的父親坂下啟二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坂下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫坂下  是天音的粉絲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.80,0:04:38.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,坂下部長的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.17,0:04:48.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作為遺屬代表來制裁你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:56.00,TXTD,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(192,546)}1小時前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說到底鮪魚超人究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要說幾次你才懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鮪魚超人是守護人類和平的正義戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說的這些聽多少遍都不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是人還是魚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:15.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,榊小姐  出門的時候要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  怎麼說我也是死了的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:22.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.10,0:05:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請問周防天音在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天姐和爸爸開車出去兜風了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要他們帶我去  結果被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那兩個人要真正搞上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:40.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.72,0:05:43.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀  去約會了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  您是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫坂下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:59.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  各位能先換下衣服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要襲擊大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要找的人是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之麻煩你快點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁著你朋友還平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的金髮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快把手機拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  為什麼要拿走我的手機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我等著你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:45.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對方攜帶著武器  支援就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是需要我們出馬的事件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去拜託警察如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:07:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,警察介入的話  由美子還活著的事就會暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:04.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被榊道昭發現的話  不是會變得很麻煩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心  作戰會在你的權限範圍內進行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二你到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.55,0:07:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,學校真是棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千秋如果還活著的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定在這樣的教室裡學習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和朋友一起增進友誼  享受著人生才對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事情我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過你做這種事又有什麼用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你想說我做的都是白費力氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你能明白突然失去女兒的父親是什麼心情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是多麼的心痛  多麼痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  這不是一回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:13.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一  清  二  楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他已經瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  這是怎麼回事啊  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}（清掃中  禁止進入）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人潛伏在三樓的空教室內
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.74,0:08:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,武器是獵槍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,窗戶被窗簾所遮擋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,內部情況不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是打掃垃圾  潛入各種地方做清掃活動的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所謂的髒活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別想多餘的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:08:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,犯人和人質在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一般情況  我們會從窗戶對他進行狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  請別在學生面前進行狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:08.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想辦法和他談判一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:12.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,校舍四周被高牆所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,附近沒有高層建築
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:18.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,後方是大海  就狙擊而言非常困難
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次就用其他的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.27,0:09:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能狙擊的話  把他引誘出來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還有一個能狙擊的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:27.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,入學第一天所看到的  換氣用的小窗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從哪裡進行射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,高台上有個燈塔  從那裡瞄準
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,離這可有900米啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:46.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快點進行確認
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.39,0:09:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是從燈塔傳來的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.85,0:09:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,射界最多只有10厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,射界15厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,4年前在射界15厘米的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狙擊了躲在被障礙物包圍的餐廳內的恐怖份子的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是麻子的傳說之一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.23,0:10:14.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把犯人引到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家便不會看到狙擊的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你很清楚我的技術吧  千鶴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請千萬別讓學生們受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算把犯人引誘到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他不用右邊數過來的第二個便池
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不會進入射程
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.93,0:10:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就想辦法讓他用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:44.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人質中有一位海軍陸戰隊員  她能幫上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,摩斯電碼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三樓  男子  廁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最右邊的便池  破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:14.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在說什麼  完全不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.70,0:11:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然收到了信號就要行動  這就是海軍陸戰隊之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.93,0:11:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為緊張  肚子變得好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,痛得快要裂開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.17,0:11:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要  要拉出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我忍著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:38.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大便還是會不斷漏出來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不想我用它糊你一臉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:44.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就快點帶我去廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.71,0:11:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.52,0:11:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,滿滿也要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別  滿滿你就別跟過來了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:55.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊  我也憋不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.69,0:12:04.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,風見先生  犯人跟小蒔和滿大小姐一起去走廊了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目前我們四人沒有受到危害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有勞報告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊解決
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  這可是男廁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,進單間不就都一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  我要去女…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.12,0:12:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就在這解決吧  這裡最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是什麼嗜好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:40.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然接了命令  不過這東西要怎麼破壞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我快點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,滿滿幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:12:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,隊員完成了任務
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢啊  你磨蹭什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不快點過來的話你的好朋友們就得死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我這就去  馬上過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.71,0:13:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,周防同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能再給大家添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音  把瓶裝水帶上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爭取讓坂下多喝水
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你能控制坂下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜點用對話拖延時間直到那傢伙起尿意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的交給我就行  相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.10,0:13:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨  周防小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這些給她們補充水份  也有你的份
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請放了她們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.24,0:14:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那麼急  先換上校服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,換完我們再商量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.45,0:14:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,商量？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.34,0:14:32.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要商量什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.61,0:14:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我家千晶被分屍埋在了冰冷的泥土下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.59,0:14:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而你卻在新同學的關懷中享受校園生活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至還交上了男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太不公平了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:56.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是犧牲了朋友活下來的醜惡毒蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:15:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你有那麼一絲悔改之心就證明給我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.78,0:15:05.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你願意在這讓我射死  我就放了那四人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:09.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若你選擇讓我射死她們四人的話  我就放了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.23,0:15:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  你要不要再次犧牲朋友苟且偷生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能射死我你就滿足了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:25.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就趕快放了她們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.13,0:15:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,周防同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋  竟敢這麼對天姐你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴  白痴  怎麼可能讓你死得那麼輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,周防同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:49.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,站起來嘛  起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這麼做完全就是拿她出氣來洩恨而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:06.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能怪天姐  遇上那種事誰能顧那麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無論事情如何  你都沒權利懲罰天音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.31,0:16:17.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  你可真是交了一群好朋友啊天音小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:21.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看來還是讓你們一起去死比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你吃什麼把身材養這麼棒的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不准逃  你這毒蟲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:46.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,JB  情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情況不明  你那邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸的手機掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:51.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要突入嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  繼續等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:17:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天音小姐  你  把千晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.56,0:17:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我過來  在殺你之前先爽一爽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.96,0:17:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我走快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,風見先生  天音小姐被帶走了  請求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,風見先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.79,0:17:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我馬上就插你個爽  給我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.65,0:17:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,JB  目標進入射界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,水喝太多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始狙擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  咦  咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我等等  畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:25.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,狙擊成功  請求捕捉犯人和救出人質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:26.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,突入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,天姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.62,0:18:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千晶  千晶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,射界10厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我追上你了嗎  麻子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.71,0:19:04.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對  這不是天音小姐的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.36,0:19:11.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也惹過不少麻煩  彼此彼此啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,話說  到底是誰救了我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.21,0:19:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.77,0:19:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然周防小姐受了一點傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過沒什麼大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.01,0:19:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了  風見同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,千鶴  不對  校長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.58,0:19:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道這算不算普通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我可以肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡就是我的學校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雄二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  不准偷跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回來  小雄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事我就回房上網了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又上網？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.03,0:20:10.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定又是通宵收黃圖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想收就收關你什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  她承認了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不准無視我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:29.59,zhushi,,0,0,0,,八重山群島：琉球群島西部的群島，位於釣魚台群島以南，宮古群島以西。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:29.59,TXTD,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fs25\an1\pos(264,575.333)}1年後\N八重山群島  與那國附近海域
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,警告目的不明艦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是日本海上保安廳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,貴艦涉嫌侵犯日本領海  請立即停船
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重複一遍  請立即停船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.54,0:22:40.22,TXTGb,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fs60\pos(640,548)}下回預告
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:45.99,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an7\fad(200,200)\blur4}話說  我們基本上都不知道\N有關雄二過去的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:44.27,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an3\fad(200,200)\blur4}站起來  站起來啊\N鮪魚超人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.14,0:22:47.39,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an1\fad(200,200)\blur4}什麼  誰習慣孤零零了\N而且我本來就不是孤零零
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.60,0:22:47.56,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8\fad(200,200)\blur4}現在將開始加油和交換人質
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:51.67,TXTGa,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an4\fad(200,200)\blur4\pos(68,249.333)}履歷我看過了\N這年代不至於\N還需要用手寫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.40,0:22:52.17,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an8\fad(200,200)\blur4}第一個由你來上\N拜託你用第一發\N使犯人喪失行動能力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:52.47,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an2\fad(200,200)\blur4}軍人不允許說不可能這個詞\N沒有軍人做不到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.48,0:22:54.63,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an3\fad(200,200)\blur4}嘿  能聽到嗎迴旋鏢\N觀測裝置設置完畢  資料傳到你PC上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.71,0:22:56.72,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an2\fad(200,200)\blur4}我專門把你從日本叫過來\N可別給我丢臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.94,0:22:59.32,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an7\fad(200,200)\blur4}我小嶺幸\N想給繁忙至極的風見先生\N獻上自己的微薄之力\N正在為其打掃房間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.41,0:22:56.70,TXTGa,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an4\fad(200,200)\blur4\pos(36,210.667)}莫非是找到了發霉的內褲？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.61,0:23:01.09,TXTGa,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an6\fad(200,200)\blur4\pos(1246.67,464)}不  是更驚人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.58,0:23:00.56,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an1\fad(200,200)\blur4}解除射擊限制\N重複一遍  解除射擊限制
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:23:02.53,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an3\fad(200,200)\blur4}你姐姐的死\N有一些可疑之處
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.33,0:23:06.14,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}喲  小弟\N這位小姐一口日語  在生什麼氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.18,0:23:07.22,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an7\fad(200,200)\blur4}你總是這樣什麼都不說\N要是覺得難受你可以跟我說的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:05.05,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an4\fad(200,200)\blur4}吶  雄二\N來玩接球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.84,0:23:07.43,TXTGa,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an6\fad(200,200)\blur4\pos(1229.33,450.667)}一隻螞蟻也不要放過\N趕盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:09.86,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an3\fad(200,200)\blur4}什麼  你說這位小姐\N年齡比我大？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.25,0:23:19.82,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an1\fad(200,200)\blur4}我會這般深愛你這個弟弟\N從遺傳基因的角度上來看肯定是正確的\N要不就是遺傳基因發生了異常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:12.15,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an4\fad(200,200)\blur4}殺了嗎  哈哈哈哈哈\N你挺能幹的嘛雄二  你真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.40,0:23:19.04,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an4\fad(200,200)\blur4}這就對了  雄二  你做對了\N這才是人類與生俱來的本能
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.55,0:23:18.95,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}對於您救了我這件事我非常感謝\N不過  我想抗議一下  您就不能選擇其他更好一點的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.12,0:23:21.36,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur4}早上好  小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.90,0:23:24.72,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur4}咦  是小弟弟  嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.23,0:23:32.10,TXTG,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}或許我是想在普通的學校  過著普通的學生生活
